Class RadarChain

    Represents the chain of a place. For more information about Places, see https://radar.io/documentation/places.

                  java.lang.String name,

        Represents the chain of a place. For more information about Places, see https://radar.io/documentation/places.

        Parameters:
        slug - The unique ID of the chain. For a full list of chains, see https://radar.io/documentation/places/chains.
        name - The name of the chain. For a full list of chains, see https://radar.io/documentation/places/chains.
        externalId - The external ID of the chain.
        metadata - The optional set of custom key-value pairs for the chain.
